snippet.title: Winter's Trumpet
snippet.description:
You can currently get it on Itchio: https://sunlabyrinth.itch.io/winterstrumpet

Winter's Trumpet is a short interactive story game (point and click format) set just a year before the events of my previous visual novel, Asher ( https://www.sunlabyrinth.com/asher-remake/ )


CC BY music by Tungerman: https://tungerman.itch.io
